  "texts": [
    "Finally, we explore emotional intelligent perception for transferring emotions to a robot.",
    "We review some recent advances in the above three areas; then, we discuss the future directions of these fields and their role in human-robot interaction.Effective Human-Robot Collaboration (HRC) integrates human skills and robotic capabilities for tasks requiring joint effort, such as co-manipulation and haptic interaction.",
    "Advances in this area are leading to more user-friendly robots, capable of tasks like assisting with manual labor or workspace organization.",
    "Additionally, Brain-Computer Interfaces (BCI) are evolving as vital tools in HRI, enabling direct communication between humans and machines through brain signals [2].",
    "Moreover, according to multiple research studies [3,4], nonverbal elements convey two-thirds of human communications."
  ]
}